data.description: Beautiful spacious, move-in ready home with plenty of yard space located in highly sought after neighborhood in Carson City. Neighbors are very friendly and our kids love the neighborhood. Close to schools, stores, parks and freeway. So many renovations and upgrades (newer roof, newer stainless steel appliances, new AC, new furnace, new pavers patio, new gaslined stone firepit with stone bench, new patio cover, new sliding doors, new concrete driveway, new sprinkler system and sod) All professionally done! We put a lot of work and love into this house for our family and its everything we wanted and more.  Due to unforseen circumstances our family will be moving.
